	units are in real-time divisions for the grace note. 
-->
<!ELEMENT cue EMPTY>
<!ELEMENT grace EMPTY>
<!ATTLIST grace
    steal-time-previous CDATA #IMPLIED
    steal-time-following CDATA #IMPLIED
    make-time CDATA #IMPLIED
